data.description: Price reduced to makes this an attractive purchase opportunity in today's market. Discover an exceptional chance to own a charming home in the heart of Brooksville.  Nestled on a generously sized corner lot spanning approximately 0.33 acres, this property offers an abundance of space for a multitude of uses. Whether you have toys, pets, or plan to host numerous family gatherings, this property's expansive grounds provide the versatility you seek. Convenience is at your doorstep with this property's proximity to downtown Brooksville, local shopping centers, nearby parks, and government facilities. Enjoy easy access to all the amenities and services the area has to offer. The residence exudes a cozy cabin-style charm and features 2 bathrooms, 3 bedrooms, a dedicated laundry room, and three exit doors, ensuring both comfort and functionality. The layout is designed to cater to your lifestyle needs. Adding to the property's allure is the presence of a tranquil small stream nearby, enhancing the picturesque country setting and providing a serene backdrop to your daily life. Recent upgrades include a brand-new A/C unit installed in 2023 and a durable metal roof. These improvements not only enhance comfort but also contribute to the long-term sustainability of the property. Located in a serene and traffic-free neighborhood, this property offers a peaceful and secure environment for your family. Schedule a viewing to experience its charm firsthand and explore the possibilities it holds for your family's future. Sellers are motivated bring best offer.
